{"tid":2151874,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"世界最狂建築物","createTime":"2020-08-11T15:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T15:58:42.000Z","uid":153217,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7a804e160409684fc7c937e17cd9349b328bffc9","tid":2151874,"uid":153217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:26:09.000Z","msg":"世界上有很多讓人驚嘆的自然景觀，也有令人著迷的壯觀建築。近年來設計師們的腦洞越來越大，將建築與工藝、時尚結合起來，建成了一座又一座奇特的建築。古人一定想不到，人類憑自己的力量就能完成這麼宏偉的工程。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡濱海灣金沙藝術科學博物館<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KT3Fg2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KT3Fg2.jpg&h=3af6785b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這座蓮花狀的建築是新加坡最知名的景點之一，於2011年2月19日首次向公眾開放。金沙集團認為，狀似蓮花盛開的博物館和三座主建築物互相輝映，將成為本地具有代表性的地標。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n西班牙La Muralla Roja<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2vrs6W6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2vrs6W6.jpg&h=9ada383b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P0iK9ar.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP0iK9ar.jpg&h=04d5f0a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這座建築就像層層堆疊的積木，看起來很可愛。<br />\n<br />\n瑞典的Emporia購物中心<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iSn76Xe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiSn76Xe.jpg&h=372bc149&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這是斯堪地那維亞最大的購物中心，有弧度的玻璃在陽光下格外璀璨，還能看到裡面的手扶梯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿塞拜疆巴庫的蓋達爾&middot;阿利耶夫中心<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2maUMXi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2maUMXi.jpg&h=81ad0b0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這是由女建築師Zaha Hadid設計的，流線型的外觀很有活力。據說這位設計師很愛&ldquo;異形&rdquo;建築，這也是她的靈感來源。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n西班牙藝術與科學之城<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eaCgfQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeaCgfQE.jpg&h=681a5d77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這座建築充滿未來感，就像露出水面的巨大骨架。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比利時原子塔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Q1EdCt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Q1EdCt.jpg&h=bbb82abc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n它的外觀就像巨大雕塑，但內部有餐廳、觀景台等等，還能透過連接的管子移動到不同的地點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭方塊屋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u9Rg0hw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu9Rg0hw.jpg&h=3becf012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這座建築就像魔術方塊一樣，基座是六邊型的，房子整體向街道傾斜，從天空俯瞰是星星般的結構。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n印度蓮花寺<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qwPa4Kf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqwPa4Kf.jpg&h=63239967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這是一座巴哈伊信仰的寺廟，不過其他信仰的人也能進去參觀。建築有9個通往中心大殿的門，代表所有宗教的融合。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿爾卑斯山旅館<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQXW0hC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQXW0hC.jpg&h=54044c6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這座建築鑲嵌在高聳的阿爾卑斯山上，被稱為&ldquo;上帝遺落的寶石&rdquo;。不過現在這間旅館還沒有建好，正處於概念構想階段。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n奧地利的格拉茨美術館<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/snVQ4Km.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsnVQ4Km.jpg&h=2be20352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這座建築被稱為&ldquo;友善的外星人&rdquo;。有人以為它的設計概念是巨型鯨魚，其實是一艘飛船。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n西班牙古根海姆博物館<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s3GQkhJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs3GQkhJ.jpg&h=f229fd22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n建築師Philip Johnson曾大贊這座建築是&ldquo;這個時代最偉大的建築&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭市場大樓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fV4qTCV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfV4qTCV.jpg&h=64e4fb12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大廳的拱形內部是漂亮的藝術投影，內容豐富多彩，有水果、蔬菜、魚和花等等。遠遠看去它就像美麗的藝術品，就連荷蘭女王就曾前來參加它的開幕式。 &lt;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿聯酋阿布扎比首都之門<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KaonVRh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKaonVRh.jpg&h=3b9e11a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大樓傾斜18度，是金氏世界紀錄認證的&ldquo;世界最傾斜的人造塔&rdquo;。著名的比薩斜塔傾斜度只有4度。<br />\n<br />\n隨著科技和建造技術的進步，設計師們從大膽的幻想，到一步步的實現，美感十足的建築物越來越多。這些炫酷的建築，也成了當地文化的代表！"},{"pid":"d052491f0560b7494539e7d291d36404f0c294e0","tid":2151874,"uid":300212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:29:10.000Z","msg":"LM 幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f06ef7610288872cd6b90ea95bc2bb9ec44746","tid":2151874,"uid":153217,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:29:28.000Z","msg":"阿爾卑斯山旅館  堅糸想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db429eb9806ab863e2bdec736e58a0707b55a117","tid":2151874,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:44:12.000Z","msg":"好L靚<br />\n建築師好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3e78e621cb6e146bdd254cf8f9cee91d380fa2","tid":2151874,"uid":7078,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:46:12.000Z","msg":"<strong>天津大爆炸遺址</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KULp9f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKULp9f9.jpg&h=a5cc4dae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成龍曾讚嘆：中国的會爆炸"},{"pid":"1988004ba8357f7ba3076e3015e2f78c6fdc39fb","tid":2151874,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:46:35.000Z","msg":"無中國福祿壽？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa4090f38508b335c65b07bec09e5483ba6a8a6","tid":2151874,"uid":212605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:49:13.000Z","msg":"一個中國建築物都冇，因為中共起建築物唔會有美感，冇創意，正係識抄"},{"pid":"bec1d31920aaebd06606a78ee7fe0c2b91b10df3","tid":2151874,"uid":153217,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:50:56.000Z","msg":"真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://chymomore.com/blog/la-muralla-roja-engagement-session-in-south-spain-ting-amp-frank\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchymomore.com%2Fblog%2Fla-muralla-roja-engagement-session-in-south-spain-ting-amp-frank&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=a6a88eff\" target=\"_blank\">https://chymomore.com/blog/la-muralla-roja-engagement-session-in-south-spain-ting-amp-frank</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0WyK9jG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0WyK9jG.jpg&h=b8e88db7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不談玄學，衹爲分享"},{"pid":"cadf169136b5db7ccab41b2cadcba802eb616df7","tid":2151874,"uid":53248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:53:19.000Z","msg":"正版舉鐵係唔係已經仙遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441cfa42c7653c2859ebd10c5aaea52e7c047d44","tid":2151874,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:55:39.000Z","msg":"福祿壽酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5189aa00d55a77489c0cf763b0dddb0b3aca938a","tid":2151874,"uid":254596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:58:42.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}